title: Campeonato Paulista Série B3
text: Campeonato Paulista Série B3 was the sixth level of the <a href="S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%20%28state%29">São Paulo</a> state professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> championship, one of the <a href="Brazilian%20Football%20State%20Championship">Brazilian state championship</a>s.
